  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/c3ea4015d7a5b6974971bd7694441b85.avif?t=1734060694\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras_big/c3ea4015d7a5b6974971bd7694441b85.avif?t=1734060694 width=800 height=374 /></span>Gunslinger Express is a top down roguelike set in the Wild West where you defend a moving train through the country. Survive as long as you can hopping between wagons to fend off enemies and protect valuable cargo. Each wagon offers unique features, such as ammo storage, medical aid, and upgrades, which you must maintain and repair to ensure your survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/d36c430baec68b749f245eb27bf6cd4d.poster.avif?t=1734060694\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/d36c430baec68b749f245eb27bf6cd4d.webm?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/d36c430baec68b749f245eb27bf6cd4d.mp4?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR CHARACTER WITH GUNS, BUFFS AND COMPANIONS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the opportunity between waves to upgrade and prepare your loadout to protect the cargo even better.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/76f984195ac79403d7d1db18be372ff1.poster.avif?t=1734060694\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/76f984195ac79403d7d1db18be372ff1.webm?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/76f984195ac79403d7d1db18be372ff1.mp4?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT ENEMIES DURING RANDOMIZED EVENTS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ambushes, sandstorms, snowfall, heavy storms & more are all randomized events that provide an extra layer of challenges during your playthrough!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/94696fd3be318ead4501a126619f476f.poster.avif?t=1734060694\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/94696fd3be318ead4501a126619f476f.webm?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/94696fd3be318ead4501a126619f476f.mp4?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/c3ea4015d7a5b6974971bd7694441b85.avif?t=1734060694\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras_big/c3ea4015d7a5b6974971bd7694441b85.avif?t=1734060694 width=800 height=374 /></span>Gunslinger Express is a top down roguelike set in the Wild West where you defend a moving train through the country. Survive as long as you can hopping between wagons to fend off enemies and protect valuable cargo. Each wagon offers unique features, such as ammo storage, medical aid, and upgrades, which you must maintain and repair to ensure your survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/d36c430baec68b749f245eb27bf6cd4d.poster.avif?t=1734060694\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/d36c430baec68b749f245eb27bf6cd4d.webm?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/d36c430baec68b749f245eb27bf6cd4d.mp4?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR CHARACTER WITH GUNS, BUFFS AND COMPANIONS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the opportunity between waves to upgrade and prepare your loadout to protect the cargo even better.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/76f984195ac79403d7d1db18be372ff1.poster.avif?t=1734060694\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/76f984195ac79403d7d1db18be372ff1.webm?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/76f984195ac79403d7d1db18be372ff1.mp4?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT ENEMIES DURING RANDOMIZED EVENTS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ambushes, sandstorms, snowfall, heavy storms & more are all randomized events that provide an extra layer of challenges during your playthrough!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/94696fd3be318ead4501a126619f476f.poster.avif?t=1734060694\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/94696fd3be318ead4501a126619f476f.webm?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507040/extras/94696fd3be318ead4501a126619f476f.mp4?t=1734060694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
